                     <interp inst="t17831029-20-verdict110" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder40s"></interp>
               GUILTY Of stealing to the value of 30 s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>To be <rs id="t17831029-20-punish111" type="punishmentDescription">
